    "description": "黑暗时代结束，英雄们成立了公会，从此消灭怪物的收费标准更加透明，还能提供对应的收据。<br><br>你将扮演一名陛下任命的卫兵，与一名妖精搭档张贴悬赏，委托英雄们调查怪事、处理怪物。你的岗位自负盈亏，责任重大，想要维持下去就得利用手头的一点权力开源节流：不管是处理商路事件控制货物涨跌，还是克扣赏金贩卖装备，甚至赌博、钓鱼、贪污……<br><br>而在辛苦工作、养家糊口外，你不仅要决定如何影响主线剧情以推进不同的结局，还得在形形色色的支线剧情中做出选择、维持各大势力支持度，以保证自己存活下去不被开除或暗杀。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/623b8b8f727b334c391c187bd6c0546f.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏详情</h2><br>◆这是一款带有经营元素的模拟+剧情游戏，每一周目剧情都将从三条主线与近百条支线中随机生成。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/8b3ec959575db1e72400c21b837f4697.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>◆卫兵模拟，处理悬赏与公务，应对各色人等的要求，克扣赏金讨价还价<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/b25209da93b63b38a3b97a36a34d5141.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>◆进入酒馆：与各个npc打交道以雇佣英雄，操纵装备商店，调节势力矛盾……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/c052585b8c208ec09f8345d35083d0f5.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>◆摸鱼钓鱼<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/c4cdf222b417edbad5e88a4c4db61db0.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>◆休假回家，养家糊口，处理家庭事务<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/23469f11a4fa376f3f58d3efcdcea7dd.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>◆探索城市：在黑市倒买倒卖，或在竞技场与赌场大发横财，探索其他秘密……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/d3c9b8977f4d22d8452dd9d1abf2cdb6.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>◆完成众多故事结局，获取蝴蝶解锁城市景观、音乐、特殊剧情、下一周目额外增益<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/dcd4cbe7a131795edc0619cfd95a0189.poster.avif?t=1719728817\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/dcd4cbe7a131795edc0619cfd95a0189.webm?t=1719728817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536470/extras/dcd4cbe7a131795edc0619cfd95a0189.mp4?t=1719728817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
